name: The Computer Did This
description: While mashing pixels around in spinning circles, I introduced a bug which produced this moiré effect. Before fixing it, I took a detour to play around with the glitch. I've talked a lot recently about how creating generative art feels like collaborating with the computer, and this piece is a prime example. | Amy Goodchild | Twitter - @amygoodchild | Instagram - @amy_goodchild | www.amygoodchild.com | 5600 x 5600 png
